org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.deploy
Class AeDeploymentFactoryImpl

java.lang.Object
  org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.deploy.AeDeploymentFactoryImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
IAeDeploymentFactory
public class AeDeploymentFactoryImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements IAeDeploymentFactory

Default IAeDeploymentFactory impl. Gets all of its deployer impls from the config map. None of its deployers should contain any state info (as they are all treated like singeltons).
